transcript:

Customer: Hello? Haan ji, main keh rahi hu aapke paas mail gaya hai kya meeting ko?
Executive: Mail mail aaya hai mere paas. Ek minute mera ye laptop restart ho raha hai isliye isme join kar raha hu. 
Customer: Haan haan koi nahi koi nahi. Main bas confirm kar rahi hu. Koi nahi main meeting mein hi hu aap join kar lo phir.
Executive: Theek hai theek hai.
Customer: Haan ji, okay.
